64
00:07:46,246 --> 00:07:49,409
And now a Blue 5 Net
exclusive interview !

65
00:07:49,816 --> 00:07:53,081
You were the first man on-site
during the aid, is that correct ?

66
00:07:53,119 --> 00:07:56,520
Yes, ma'am. The first one in
and the last one out.

67
00:07:58,458 --> 00:08:02,087
Were the robots so dangerous
that you needed to use guns ?

68
00:08:03,129 --> 00:08:07,725
The only survivors were 8 of my men
and just 3 of the plant's personnel.

69
00:08:07,767 --> 00:08:10,235
We tried our best.

70
00:08:11,104 --> 00:08:15,165
Are you on the side of the humans ?
Or are you on the side of the robots ?

71
00:08:15,208 --> 00:08:17,472
My own beliefs
guide my actions.

72
00:08:17,510 --> 00:08:20,673
Humans are humans
and robots are robots.

73
00:08:21,748 --> 00:08:24,444
Human rights are reserved
for humans only, I'd say.

74
00:08:24,951 --> 00:08:28,751
Thank you for your time.
That was Colonel Strings.

75
