is enjoying a nice drink !

80
00:10:52,398 --> 00:10:53,387
What the...?!

81
00:10:56,502 --> 00:10:57,491
BOO !

82
00:11:19,859 --> 00:11:24,887
A Second, enhanced for hand-
to-hand combat. Handmade...

83
00:11:25,531 --> 00:11:28,762
You're not human, are you ?

84
00:11:28,801 --> 00:11:32,567
